  "text": "HUVEC (Clonetics TM Human umbilical vascular endothelial cells, Cambrex) were cultured in EGM TM Bullet kit (CC-3124) containing 500 ml Endothelial Cell Basal Medium supplemented with 2 ml Bovine Brain extract, 0.5 ml human epidermal growth factor (hEGF), 0.5 ml hydrocortisone, 10 ml fetal calf serum and 0.5 ml GA-1000 (Gentamicin, Amphotericin). The cell line was cultivated at 37 °C, 95% humidity and 5% CO 2 and used between passages 4 and 12 [CITATION_1] .",
